data.description: This home has two living spaces. One bedroom, bath, living area and kitchen upstairs . One bedroom, bath, living space and kitchen space downstairs. 3rd bedroom possible.  Property is on a septic system and community well. Heating is provided by wood burning and pellet stoves and gas furnace. 2 year old window AC unit upstairs. Existing appliances included.   New 30 year roof approximately 16 months old. Covered porch with Views of Walker Lake, NV.
